          "language": "en",
          "name": "Content Repurposer",
          "description": "Transforms single content pieces into multiple formats for different platforms. Analyzes source content, adapts for various platforms, generates diverse formats, and creates strategic publishing schedules to maximize content ROI and reach.",
          "instructions": "Provide your source content and specify the target formats you want to create. Optionally include platform-specific requirements. The routine will analyze your content, create multiple adapted versions, and provide a strategic content calendar for publication.",
          "details": "This routine helps content creators maximize the value of their work by systematically repurposing single pieces into multiple formats. It maintains core messaging while adapting tone, length, and format for different platforms and audiences, significantly extending content reach and engagement."
